_dataGuide.note: For mass updates, use these primary arrays:

primaryArrays.envelopes: Main envelope data - edit currentBalance, name, category, etc.
primaryArrays.bills: Bill payment data - edit amount, dueDate, provider, etc.
primaryArrays.debts: Debt tracking data - edit currentBalance, minimumPayment, etc.
primaryArrays.savingsGoals: Savings goal data - edit targetAmount, currentAmount, etc.
primaryArrays.allTransactions: All transactions + bills combined (auto-generated, don't edit directly)
primaryArrays.auditLog: Change history and audit trail (generally shouldn't be edited)

deprecatedArrays.note: These may exist from old exports but are not actively used in v1.8+

_dataGuide.importInstructions: Edit 'envelopes', 'bills', or 'transactions' arrays, then re-import. The app will rebuild 'allTransactions' automatically.

connections.Debt Bill: bills have debtId field pointing to debt
connections.Transaction Bill: bill payment transactions have billId field
